  "headline": "CSS Flexbox",
  "description": "Flexbox provides one-dimensional layout (row or column), distributing space and aligning items within a container. `display: flex` on parent enables flex context. Key properties: `justify-content` (main axis alignment), `align-items` (cross axis), `flex-grow/shrink/basis` (item sizing).",
